Usher think out things that are original in character. These may take widely diverse forms. Usher might invent some very ingenious contrivance or evolve a new method. Whatever it is, the world will be taken a step forward on Usher's account.There is no doubt that Usher set great score on honesty, using the term in its widest sense. Usher require Usher's friends to be honest in purpose, honest in speech, as well as in money affairs.Usher's greatest weakness lies in the way Usher treat others. Usher cannot tolerate inefficiency and Usher are apt to consider those who do not see eye to eye with Usher as being hopelessly beneath contempt. It would not be difficult for Usher to cultivate a more charitable and tolerant view towards those who are likely to earn Usher's disapproval. At any rate, it is well worth trying.Usher are a person of considerable action. Usher are never still. Usher are always making plans and the thing Usher can least tolerate is inactivity. Usher have much self will, and the spirit of independence is firmly planted in Usher. Usher resent the interference of others, perhaps more than Usher should, and freedom is a quality Usher prize very highly- freedom not only of action but also of thought.

Usher are a person who live in fantasy. Hypersensitive, many of Usher have inferiority complexes, feeling slighted by taking the most unrelated incident as personal insult. It is important that Usher do not indulge in drugs or alcohol, for this adds to Usher's unclarity. Usher be honest with Usher'sself and others, and attempt to be as realistic as possible, for Usher tend toward escapism. Music, colours and nature are very positive in smoothing Usher's overly sensitive being.Usher are a sensible person by nature, which will also help Usher to handle various situations in life. Usher are likely to experience obstacles in Usher's studies but will face each and every situation without succumbing to fear. Usher's urge to acquire more and more knowledge will help Usher climb the ladder of success. In the initial phase of Usher's life, Usher may encounter certain difficulties, but Usher will prove to be lucky in Usher's studies solely because of Usher's concentration skills. Sometimes, Usher may find it difficult to remember certain things, but thinking hard during such time can make everything crystal clear. This aspect of Usher's character will help Usher to succeed in the realm of Usher's studies.

Children will give Usher tremendous motivation to set goals and accomplish them. Usher feel a responsibility to them and must not let them down. Use this motivating factor to its fullest, but be sure that Usher's are doing what Usher want to do and not directing Usher's efforts in an area which Usher do not like just because of Usher's sense of responsibility.
